<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mwạʿydy lyk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (mwạʿydy lyk fy ạlạ̉kẖṭạr .. ʿyny ʿlyk
 fy ạllyl wfy ạlnhạr .. ʿyny ʿlyk)2
 wạnt fy ʿmq ạlbḥạr .. ʿyny ʿlyk
 mwạʿydy lyk fy ạlạ̉kẖṭạr .. fy ạllyl wfy ạlnhạr
 wạnt fy ʿmq ạlbḥạr
 ạlqrạr- (ʿyny ʿlyk yạ bny ʿly̱ ṭwl)2
 2- (fy ạlwdyạn wfy ạljbạl .. ʿyny ʿlyk
 fy ạlḥl wfy ạltrḥạl .. ʿyny ʿlyk)2
 fy ạlmṣạʿb wạlạ̉hwạl .. ʿyny ʿlyk
 fy ạlwdyạn wfy ạljbạl .. fy ạlḥl wfy ạltrḥạl
 fy ạlmṣạʿb wạlạ̉hwạl
 3- (wạ̹nt bʿyd .. wạ̹nt qryb .. ʿyny ʿlyk
 fy ạlrḥlẗ .. wạ̹nt gẖryb .. ʿyny ʿlyk)2
 ḥty̱ fy ạlẓrf ạlʿṣyb .. ʿyny ʿlyk
 wạ̹nt bʿyd wạ̹nt qryb .. fy ạlrḥlẗ wạ̹nt gẖryb
 ḥty̱ fy ạlẓrf ạlʿṣyb
 4- (ạ̉nạ mʿạk .. yạ ạbny ʿly̱ ṭwl .. ʿyny ʿlyk
 mạtkẖạfsẖ .. mn ạlmjhwl .. ʿyny ʿlyk)2
 fy ạlʿwạṣf wạlsywl .. ʿyny ʿlyk
 ạ̉nạ mʿạk yạ ạbny ʿly̱ ṭwl .. mạtkẖạfsẖ mn ạlmjhwl
 fy ạlʿwạṣf wạlsywl</lyrics>
